long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension will move Wikipedia pages to the top of your Google search results

This is a fixed version of https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/make-wikipedia-1/ckmmohmhhpeemgpjanclllmmdajomdkc. A change in the google search page broke it. I have reached out to the author on GitHub but i have not had a response. I am uploading this so I can have it on all my devices without manually loading the unpacked extension.
